title: Perfume Genius - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Perfume Genius performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded November 15, 2021.

Songs:
Without You
Jason
On The Floor
Nothing At All 

Mike Hadreas - Lead Vocals
Alan Wyffles - Keys
Meg Duffy - Guitar

Tim Carr - Drums 
Patrick Kelly - Bass

Host: Cheryl Waters
